'''Fabulous 103fm''' is a [[radio station]] in [[Pattaya]], [[Thailand]]. It has been [[broadcasting]] in the English language since 2012, and is licensed by the Broadcasting Committee of Thailand to broadcast on [[FM broadcasting|FM]]. With limited signal imposed under licensing laws, Fabulous 103 also transmits on the internet via its website and is available via most applications, such as [[TuneIn|tunein]].

Shows on Fabulous 103 include those of radio legends [[Emperor Rosko]], [[David Hamilton (broadcaster)|David Hamilton]] and [[Pat Sharp]], alongside [[Gary King (radio)|Gary King]] and Tommy Dee who runs the morning show.

