'''Socialist Youth of Northern Rhodesia''' was a youth organisation in [[Northern Rhodesia]] (present-day [[Zambia]]). It was a member of the [[International Union of Socialist Youth]].<ref name="p3">Braunthal, Julius (ed). ''Yearbook of the International Socialist Labour Movement''. Vol. II. London: Lincolns-Prager International Yearbook Pub. Co, 1960. p. 44</ref>

